Mike S. Zafirovski Joins Blackstone
October 05, 2011



Share:




 



The Blackstone Group has hired Mike S. Zafirovski as a senior advisor. Mr. Zafirovski has also been appointed as a member of the Board of Directors of Apria Healthcare Group, which was taken private by Blackstone in 2008. Mr. Zafirovski has previously worked at Nortel, Motorola and General Electric.





